# loc-guardian: exclude generated/handoff artifacts and test files
# whose paths the skill's hard-coded patterns miss.

# Design-handoff artifacts (Figma export, never edited by hand).
design_handoff_claudepot/

# Lock file (defense in depth — already in tokei defaults).
pnpm-lock.yaml

# Integration test crates — the skill excludes a top-level `tests/`
# directory but tokei's `--exclude tests` does not consistently match
# `crates/*/tests/` paths.
crates/*/tests/

# Inline-included test modules. Loaded via `#[cfg(test)] #[path]` from
# a production sibling so they retain `super::*` access to private
# items. The skill's exclude glob is `*_test.*` (singular); we use the
# `_tests.rs` plural to mirror the inline `mod tests` convention.
**/*_tests.rs
